   * Creates a space
   * @memberof ClientAPI
   * @see {Space.Space}
   * @param {object} data - Object representation of the Space to be created
   * @param {string=} organizationId - Organization ID, if the associated token can manage more than one organization.

   * .then(space => console.log(space))
